<p style="text-align:start">Bay Path offers a wide range of amenities and services including a Barber Shop, musical entertainment, shopping excursions, field trips and onsite activities.</p>  <p style="text-align:start"><br /> Social services counseling and discharge planning are important elements of the care and services Bay Path Rehabilitation &amp; Nursing Center provides. Social workers help to identify a resident&rsquo;s psychosocial, mental and emotional needs and then develop individualized plans to meet those needs. Discharge planners define additional services and follow-up resources necessary to ensure a smooth transition from the nursing center home.<br /> &nbsp;</p>  <p style="text-align:start">Nearby continuum of care options for residents of Bay Path include Allerton House&nbsp;Assisted Living&nbsp;at The Village at Duxbury, Independent Living at The Village,&nbsp;and&nbsp;The Garden Homes.&nbsp;</p>  <p style="text-align:start"><br /> <strong>Clinical Services at Bay Path</strong><br /> &nbsp;</p>  <ul style="list-style-type:disc; margin-left:40px"> 	<li>Admissions 24/7</li> 	<li>Pain Management</li> 	<li>Diabetic Care and Teaching</li> 	<li>Palliative Care and Hospice</li> 	<li>Enteral Tube Feeding</li> 	<li>Physical/ Occupational/Speech and Language Therapy available 7 days/week</li> 	<li>Established Tracheostomy</li> 	<li>Indwelling Catheters</li> 	<li>IV Therapy/Central Line Management</li> 	<li>Wound Care/Wound Vac</li> 	<li>Ostomy Care<br /> 	&nbsp;</li> </ul>  <p style="text-align:start"><strong>Individual Care at Bay Path</strong><br /> &nbsp;</p>  <ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;"> 	<li>Elective Joint Replacement</li> 	<li>Limb Loss</li> 	<li>Cancer</li> 	<li>Neurological diseases</li> 	<li>Congestive Heart Failure</li> 	<li>Pain Syndromes</li> 	<li>Diabetes</li> 	<li>Pneumonia/Bronchitis/ Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease</li> 	<li>Post-surgical Conditions</li> 	<li>Hip Fracture</li> 	<li>Stroke</li> </ul> 